@ Brussels, Belgium Beer Trip.



Aroma is malty, some biscuit, fruity and grassy hops. Taste is medium- sweet pale malt, light caramel, some biscuit, light to medium bitterness, medium- citrus lemony-orange and grassy hops, dry finish.




